  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 53 - 052\nE8\n\nBecause the 5D world depends on deep recess along the 4th spatial axis it appears very old (depth along this axis is for us time). But in fact it is exempt from time, as witness its role as transtemporal constants. But in terms of our time (the 4th axis) it is ancient + is gone; on the 4th spatial axis it is deeply recessed but still here, because when the 4th axis is converted from time to space, things don't pass away; they as the Form axes in \"Ubik\" only recede. + ",
